### 2. Get Admin Dashboard Data
# @name getDashboard
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 3. Get Sales Detail for a SPECIFIC DATE
# Ganti tanggal '2025-10-02' dengan tanggal yang ingin Anda tes.
# Format harus YYYY-MM-DD.
# @name getSpecificDateSalesDetail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/dashboard/sales-detail?date=2025-10-02
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}